{"type": "article", "id": 63560, "title": "Pandora 第一季度销售下滑 10%，以及，来看 Met Gala 最佳着装 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2019-05-07T08:59:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14878, "name": "Reformation"}, {"id": 58397, "name": "Kylie Cosmetics"}, {"id": 37058, "name": "BCBG"}, {"id": 2969, "name": "Vivienne Westwood"}, {"id": 58398, "name": "Eastpack"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/201905071653051MocagbBZSz7rGYH.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/beauty-features/kylie-cosmetics-said-to-have-had-ma-talks-1203122150/\" rel=\"nofollow\">传 Kylie Cosmetics 寻求出售</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 据 WWD 报道，Kylie Cosmetics 目前的报价为 30 亿美元。自 2015 年创立以来，该品牌发展迅速，成立 18 个月后总销售额即达到 4.2 亿美元。2017 年首次公开业绩后，有多名买家表示出兴趣。不过 Kylie Cosmetics 去年增长放缓，销售额为 3.6 亿美元，与上一年相比近增长 9%。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/financial/reformation-for-sale-in-goldman-run-process-sources-1203124516/\" rel=\"nofollow\">传美国环保女装品牌 Reformation 寻求出售</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 据 WWD 报道，主打环保及度假风的美国环保女装品牌 Reformation 目前已委托高盛银行处理出售事宜，第一轮竞购将于 5 月 15 日前完成。虽然目前未透露具体估值，但有信源向 WWD 表示“数额巨大”。</p><p>Reformation 自成立以来据称年销售额增幅维持在 50% 以上，2015 年融资 1200 万美元，随后又于 2017 年融资 2500 万美元，其中也包括&nbsp;Net-a-porter 创始人&nbsp;Natalie Massenet 参股的投资基金&nbsp;Imaginary Ventures。Reformation 主要将这些资金用于拓展实体店铺、增强洛杉矶工厂（占生产的 60%）产能。目前该品牌拥有 13 家门店，线上销售渠道则包括官网、Nordstrom 以及上个月建立合作关系的 Net-a-Porter。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/financial/pandora-q1-sales-down-turnaround-program-1203125087/\" rel=\"nofollow\">轻奢珠宝品牌 Pandora 第一季度销售额下滑 10%</a></strong> |&nbsp;截至 3 月 31 日的三个月内，Pandora 销售额下滑 10% 至 48 亿克朗（约 7.2 亿美元），净利润从去年同期的 12 亿克朗下滑至 7.97 亿克朗。今年 2 月刚上任的 CEO Alexander Lacik 表示，Pandora 作为一个成熟品牌的确遇到了一些严峻挑战，而 CFO Anders Boyer 则表示其两年转型计划正在稳步实施，一些商业试验和营销尝试已经“表现出不错的成果”。<br></p><p><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/max-azria-dead-1203124841/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>BCBG 创始人&nbsp;</strong><strong>Max Azria&nbsp;</strong><strong>去世，享年 70 岁</strong></a>&nbsp;| 据 WWD 报道，Max Azria 于本周一因肝癌在休斯敦医院去世。Max Azria 于 1989 年在美国洛杉矶创立品牌 BCBG，在快时尚商业模式流行前推动了时尚的民主化。鼎盛时期，BCBG 集团旗下拥有 BCBG Max Azria、BCBGeneration、Max Azria Atelier 以及 Hervé Léger by Max Azria 等多个品牌，在 47 个国家有 595 家门店，零售额达到 20 亿美元。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://highxtar.com/vivienne-westwood-teams-with-buffalo/?lang=en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vivienne Westwood 与有 40 年历史、以厚底鞋著称的德国鞋履品牌 Buffalo London 推出两个合作鞋款。</a></strong><br></p><p>两个鞋款分别以 Vivienne Westwood 的经1981 年鞋款&nbsp;Pirate boot 以及 2014 年鞋款&nbsp;Everything is Connected Sandal 为灵感，融合 Buffalo 的 Classics 以及 Hightower Platform 系列，均为男女均可穿的中性风。系列大片则由知名摄影师&nbsp;Jürgen Teller 拍摄<strong>。&nbsp;</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507162312u7dRPyfE4IK5hmt2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507162322wK4JTPQ2zdoc3ESN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666327\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507162234gtCcRTUo4mlSIxHE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507162250vur7FIOoj6ECQfNG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507162300bnceNvWuPYqU5r9y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071623007xTDC0MGoUe2pBkS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507162301gBZ5wzySlJ2k9fR7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071623012HcT14kSGzip6ZIq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071623549krnuJBQPAqhglCv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507162411Ktsw5lHP9CkBhcRG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507162424H7v1dqyRMSp8wDjQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071624369SkEUhd4aQygJb8s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/420820/eastpak-fabuyi-andy-warhol-weilinggandebaokuanxilie/\" rel=\"nofollow\">EASTPAK 发布以 Andy Warhol 为灵感的包款系列。</a></strong></p><p>包上的印花来自 Andy Warhol 在 1965 年创作的 <i>Colored Campbell’s Soup Can </i>，价格从 35 至 240 美元不等。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071445543piNetV8WjCswbOq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144555C9RajdLxhHMw3kzf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144554U43ydPLBHXmSWspa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://schepperheyn.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">柏林品牌 Schepperheyn 发布 2019 秋冬 Lookbook。</a></strong><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144119lFt0ITmErM8RH1aj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071441204NIOAlu5fK2xFSHJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144130fENl6mIq7ruUgsFO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144130pfvIgcasBdiSxTKn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144131sK2oJN10gl8X5GVD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144131eMClqRISEsQXJ0c2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071441314fNdIx2SiRlmwXsz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071441316BgT7xLueUA2cEY9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144132tbjIrdpw7FEByDxH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144134xPGTVyhzF5toW8lM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019050714413323HtqNJK6VkMp0Zl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144133ZtAj86hFzOBe2MrD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144133hR5wWK7fv6aElizs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144132wAjS7lCv2JTrfskx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144133ARDjQW0G1Yq9MoIk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144134z7b38xVatqXM0OGk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144134Y4rFRfzl7awon1kE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144135DSPHE5tdGQJxj4TI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071441362mvhrcsxq39wCiRu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144136x8IUBgLiF5kDKNw4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144136h2UrsPy3uNvW5zQ4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507144136HkmFbfMYhGqLZxp4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2019/05/2019-met-gala-best-dressed#&amp;gid=ci0246370230002751&amp;pid=hamish-bowles-met-gala\" rel=\"nofollow\">Met Gala 上的一些 Best Looks。</a></strong></p><p>Met Gala（纽约大都会艺术博物馆服装学院慈善晚会）于 1948 年首次举办，随后于每年五月的第一个星期一举行，主要目的是为大都会服装学院筹集资金，并庆祝其最新展览的开幕。</p><p>今年的主题为“Camp：时尚笔记”，灵感来自美国公共知识分子 Susan Sontag 1964 年论文<i> Camp: Notes on Fashion </i>（《坎普：时尚札记》）。“坎普”原本源自美国同性恋群体内部流传的黑话，指举止阴柔的女性，而 Susan Sontag 则认为其本质是对不自然事物的偏好，而这一颠覆性的审美趣味是一种政治批判的表达方式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154356ITfpmu0XyUGrqziL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.393197\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Michael Urie</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071547563o7n14OlYtmpGeHW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Ezra Miller in Burberry</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154724S0L2Zjyg6rkcxPEh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.505882\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Harry Styles in Gucci</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154357TZlxn4iAHVRueQ5X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.615142\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Katy Perry&nbsp;</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154731GDcZ28vKJr0IhkNH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Cara Delevingne in Dior Haute Couture</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154725sDC6AXlRmPne4dLk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.504891\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Abbey Lee Kershaw in Thom Browne</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154730Dl5U18J73EhcXLaP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.431639\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Aquaria in Maison Margiela</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071547311Ol2JUXAphM5Z4nQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.504891\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Celine Dion in Oscar de la Renta</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154906NL3jRZ74ydfaJ2Eh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Tracee Eliss Rose in Moschino&nbsp;</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154910ir1zVCgfK35FXPq0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Janelle Monae in Christian Siriano</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154820U3gO09qe4PrsTlBR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.504891\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Florence Welch in Gucci</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019050715490225qTXId6blS9ONer.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502630\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Lucy Boynton in Prada</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071553547oNFVvXrj0Rx2wL4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.457726\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Anna Wintour in Chanel</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154905BGHxuPi0tjwfv31Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.504891\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Saoirse Ronan in Gucci</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154902ZbxQpytI8BAERw7f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Lupita Nyon'o in Versace</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071547323eYlnZ6mA4LzwX9I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Dua Lipa in Versace</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071548565xFS6nsoTjhWcik0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.419446\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Kendall Jenner in Versace</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154857FAM7H5boa3nCGSOL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.467351\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Kylie Jenner in Versace</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507155556qV68EnIj5CQ1uyJM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Kim Kardashian in Mugler</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071549041USFv5prYyw0HOxW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Naomi Campbell in Valentino</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154900GP7v5Ise4yb2afAO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.506024\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Lena Waithe(with Kerbi Jean-Raymond) in Pyer Moss</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507155643mUWexifgqSPMzhp9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.425517\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Alessandro Michele in Gucci</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071549035lsNDHI4XA0KTaS7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Lady Gaga in Brandon Maxwell</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071548418qXoC4zJVr1hAHYU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.732000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Hamish Bowles in Maison Margiela</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154731AZVT9DvzPBpcuUw4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Cardi B in Thom Browne</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154730q85nd9mvPZYibB02.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.726500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Billy Porter in the Blonds</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190507154901qk2LRD6TNix1ESGt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.820500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Lili Reinhart in Salvatore Ferragamo&nbsp;</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201905071549068HOe1aok9Ts6Fru0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Zazie Beetz in Thom Browne</figcaption> </figure></div><p>题图为 <a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2019/05/2019-met-gala-best-dressed#&amp;gid=ci0246370230002751&amp;pid=met-gala-2019-lady-gaga-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lady Gaga at Met Gala 2019</a></p>"}